item.title: xQTL protocol data
item.description: xQTL protocol data # A toy data-set consisting of 49 de-identified samples from ROSMAP project, used to illustrates the computational protocols we developed for the detection and analysis of molecular QTLs (xQTLs). Contact # Hao Sun Location # The input data and some of the intermediate output data can be download from this Synapse folder. To download the files, a synapse account and synapse clients are both needed.
